title: Number of births in Sweden 2009 to 2019
summary: Overall Number of births has increased over the Year.
Number of births is roughly constant from 2014 to 2015, and lastly slightly increasing from 2015 to 2016.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2015 and 2016.
Maximum Number of births, about 117425.0 was reported at Year 2016
Minimum Number of births about 114870.0 was reached at Year 2015
